README file for LTRT_test_mode
August 2013

LTRT_test_mode is the default runtime code for LTRT in testing mode.


1) Upload the default sketch to Arduino (AnalogueCapture)

2) As root, chmod /dev/ttyACM0 to 777

Open 3 xterms

3) Start the capture:
$ ./analogue_capture.sh

4) Smooth the data every 5000 lines:
$ ./smooth.sh 5000

5) Plot out direct from the serial port (edit plot.gp with yrange):
$ ./plot_analogue_capture.sh
